{"tid":2201284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★保就業計劃第二期｜周日截止申請　消息：滙豐銀行續不參與","createTime":"2020-09-13T16:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T16:29:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc7034e2d179ab8676bb6ac279456431d2ad226","tid":2201284,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"政府推出第二期「保就業」計劃，周日（13日）截止申請。已獲取第一期達6.8億元工資補貼的國泰航空，日前已表明不會再申請，引發裁員恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，無參與第一期計劃的滙豐銀行，今次亦不會申請。至截稿前，滙豐仍未回覆是否會有裁員計劃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/522857/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F-%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F522857%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%259F-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=51bec26f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/522857/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F-%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%88%AA%E6%AD%A2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87</a>"},{"pid":"5f591ae3c8f8be92d0fcf99d536ece3f570cbeb7","tid":2201284,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji